{"tid":1634451,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"阿詩Tommy上街反惡法","createTime":"2019-10-07T08:02:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T11:31:31.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"be1c3cba680dbb20b6a117b69e78389532ec3651","tid":1634451,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T08:02:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20191007/20782222\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191007%2F20782222&d=fuRTyfFj%2BaUlIJflnhZSn3O0ZW31AiaZ%2BXmqixBX3cM%3D&h=3c944763\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191007%2F20782222&h=6e9bbe6f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20191007/20782222</a><br />\n<br />\n阿詩Tommy上街反惡法<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191007/large/1570368014_2d23.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191007%2Flarge%2F1570368014_2d23.jpg&h=2cf59542&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n何韻詩昨日貼在灣仔撐傘的相片，又表示為港人加油。互聯網圖片<br />\n<br />\n阮民安（Tommy）昨日走到銅鑼灣參與網民發起「10.6反緊急法大遊行」，對於網絡有片段指前晚大埔有父母帶住小朋友在街上踏單車，遭警員指他們三人非法集結，Tommy炮轟這個極權是不可理喻，昨日身穿黑衣和戴上口罩的他說：「太太話遇着屋企人唔舒服而要戴口罩，到時點呢？係咪連街都唔可以落呢？」提到有持槍的警員在醫院欲拘捕涉嫌參與非法集會的人士，Tommy大罵警方「冇人性」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191007/large/1570368013_7381.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191007%2Flarge%2F1570368013_7381.jpg&h=ac122f8a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nTommy參與遊行，大罵警方「冇人性」。<br />\n<br />\n至於何韻詩昨也有在社交網貼戴口罩在灣仔撐傘相片，阿詩留言：「我們仍然未得勝，還在革命，頑強爭取太平。#香港人加油#反惡法」。另外，港台《頭條新聞》節目主持曾志豪亦貼出戴口罩相，並留言揶揄港府「咁係咪拉硬？」<br />\n<br />\n採訪：馬建華<br />\n攝影：馮嘉銘 <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n康子妮閒逛忙撳電話<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n項明生被鬧牆頭草表忠"},{"pid":"c2778fb27ea1b9160739ccdafa972cc1a3e9da06","tid":1634451,"uid":276758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T11:31:31.000Z","msg":"題外話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n幾次見tommy仔都係大長褸,hoodie咁出黎行<br />\n其實熱唔熱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />講緊係3x度"}]}